{
  "texts": [
    "It can also be used to write research papers.",
    "It provides real-time feedback that improves document quality during the writing process.",
    "It is a grammar-checker, plagiarism-checker, and a vocabulary improvement tool.",
    "It can quickly suggest full-sentence rewrites to make a clearer and concise point.Quillbot (https://quillbot.com/): Originally designed as a paraphrasing tool, Quillbolt is now a free one-stop shop for all the various needs of manuscript writers.",
    "It includes a plethora of features, such as grammar checkers, plagiarism checkers, translators, citation generators, and summarizers."
